1. Install EMANE from https://github.com/adjacentlink/emane

2. Install dependencies with the following command:

# sudo apt-get install lxc bridge-utils mgen fping gpsd gpsd-clients \
    iperf multitail olsrd openssh-server python-tk python-pmw python-lxml \
    python-stdeb build-essential

3. Add the following lines to /etc/hosts:

10.99.0.1 node-1
10.99.0.2 node-2
10.99.0.3 node-3
10.99.0.4 node-4
10.99.0.5 node-5
10.99.0.6 node-6
10.99.0.7 node-7
10.99.0.8 node-8
10.99.0.9 node-9
10.99.0.10 node-10
10.99.0.100 node-server
10.100.0.1 radio-1
10.100.0.2 radio-2
10.100.0.3 radio-3
10.100.0.4 radio-4
10.100.0.5 radio-5
10.100.0.6 radio-6
10.100.0.7 radio-7
10.100.0.8 radio-8
10.100.0.9 radio-9
10.100.0.10 radio-10

